-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-29/former-yankee-buck-showalter-hired-as-orioles-manager-baltimore-sun-says.html

          
          
             Buck Showalter was hired as manager
of the Baltimore Orioles, putting the former field boss of the
New York Yankees in charge of the team with Major League
Baseballâ€™s worst record, the Baltimore Sun said.  
 Showalter, 54, was chosen after protracted negotiations,
the Sun said, citing two unidentified people. The Orioles are
31-70 and 33 1/2 games behind the first-place Yankees in the
American League East.  
 Mick McDonald, an Orioles spokesman, declined to confirm
